---
const links = [
  { label: "Contact", href: "/contact" },
  { label: "Partenaires", href: "/partenaires" },
  { label: "Mentions legales", href: "/mentions-legales" },
  { label: "Confidentialite", href: "/confidentialite" },
  { label: "Admin", href: "/admin" }
];
---
<footer class="bg-brand-blue text-white">
  <div class="grid h-2 w-full grid-cols-3">
    <div class="bg-flag-blue"></div>
    <div class="bg-flag-yellow"></div>
    <div class="bg-flag-red"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-8 px-4 py-12 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div>
      <a href="/" class="block mb-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <img src="/brand/logo.png" alt="Bloc Leopards" class="h-24 w-auto" />
          <img src="/brand/logo-min-sport-white.webp" alt="Ministère des Sports" class="h-16 w-auto opacity-80" />
        </div>
      </a>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Un seul bloc. Une seule voix. Mobilisation citoyenne des supporters pour une tribune positive et respectueuse.</p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-slate-400">Les annonces institutionnelles restent a verifier aupres des organismes competents.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-yellow">Navigation</p>
      <div class="grid gap-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
        {links.map((item) => (
          <a href={item.href} class="hover:text-brand-yellow transition-colors">{item.label}</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-yellow">Contacts</p>
      <div class="text-sm text-slate-300 space-y-2">
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:contact@blocaleopards.cd" class="hover:text-brand-yellow transition-colors">contact@blocaleopards.cd</a></p>
        <p>Kinshasa, RDC</p>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-slate-400">© 2026 Bloc Leopards. Tous droits reserves.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
